                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8093" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1259</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2903 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鉴往知来：三丰智能商誉暴雷事件的追因与问策</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Learning from the past: tracing the causes and asking for countermeasures of Sanfeng &#39;s goodwill thunderstorms</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨春丽，杨植林</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北三丰智能输送装备股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">24 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商誉减值；企业估值；对赌协议；并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Impairment of goodwill;Business valuation; VAM ;M&amp;A</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着建设制造强国目标的提出，国内装备制造企业为加速产品智能化转型，纷纷通过并购的方式进行资源整合。在此背景下，由并购活动带来的高额商誉减值问题频繁出现，如何识别与防范商誉减值风险已经成为公众关注的焦点问题。三丰智能早期为实现经营目标急切加入到并购热潮中，不惜以高额溢价作为筹码并购鑫燕隆，却不曾想在承诺期满后美梦幻灭，三年内连续发生两次商誉暴雷。如今，公司不仅面临着业绩承诺失灵的问题，还深陷利润操纵的舆论漩涡。本案例通过梳理三丰智能并购鑫燕隆的交易过程，挖掘三丰智能两次商誉暴雷的原因，重点指出三丰智能在商定企业估值结果和对赌协议设计上的失误，并进一步提出两次商誉暴雷背后是否存在不当的盈余管理行为等问题。案例旨在让学生了解企业并购动因，启发学生从多角度思考商誉暴雷的原因并提出防范商誉暴雷的建议。同时，寓思政于案例，引导学生在对商誉减值进行会计处理时践行“诚信、敬业”的社会主义核心价值观，培养学生的会计职业道德品质；引导学生自觉遵守《企业会计准则》等法规，增强学生的合规意识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">To build a manufacturing power, domestic equipment manufacturing companies have been accelerating their intelligent transformation through M&amp;A. However, identifying and preventing the risk of goodwill impairment resulting from corporate mergers has become public concern. Sanfeng early to achieve its business objectives, with a high price of the acquisition of Sinylon, but after three years Sanfeng suffered two goodwill thunderstorms. Now, Sanfeng is not only facing the problem of failed VAM, but also deeply involved in the public opinion vortex of surplus manipulation.This case analyzes the transaction of Sanfeng&#39;s acquisition of Sinylon, explores the reasons for Sanfeng&#39;s goodwill impairment, and focuses on the mistakes in business valuation and designing VAM. It further raises the question of whether Sanfeng management has a problem of surplus manipulation. The case aims to help students understand the motives behind corporate mergers, inspire them to think about the reasons for “goodwill thunderstorm” and propose recommendations for avoiding it. At the same time, it guides students to practice the socialist core values of &quot;integrity and dedication&quot; and cultivate their professional ethics. It also guides students to enhance compliance awareness and consciously abide by accounting standards and regulations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《高级财务会计》、《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业合并；资产减值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
